data.description: Your home at the beach is here! Welcome to 18 Brighton Street, with over 2,000 sqft of beautiful open living space, this home is upgraded and truly move-in-ready! Greeted by vaulted ceilings upon entering, you'll love the large living space complete with a gas fireplace and additional sitting area or potential dining space. The eat-in kitchen boasts new vinyl plank flooring, stainless steel appliances, new granite counter tops and is finished off with a fresh coat of paint. On the main level, the primary suite can be found at the back of the house with large closets and a spacious master bathroom. A single-car garage can be accessed through the combination laundry/mud room with a new washer and dryer installed in 2022. Upstairs are two oversized bedrooms with walk in closets, a loft space and a shared full bathroom. Outside is mature landscaping, a back deck and a fully fenced in yard. Enjoy community amenities while paying minimal HOA  fees, and take a short walk or bike ride to area restaurants, shops and beaches! 18 Brighton makes the perfect beach home, investment property or year-round residence- don't miss the opportunity to own this coastal twin home for well under 500k!
